         Think of something that a necromancer would do. </P><P>See.. there's this area.... I like to solo pull there.. but ..someone/some group... is yanking my mobs....I can't really solo with a pet now .. cause .. I'll be visible.. pulling mobs over people.. and hey, it will just aggro them , and that's real mean & lame...</P><P>SO - what to do, what to do ? </P><P>Invis up...</P><P>Go inside.</P><P>Find named. </P><P>Root it. </P><P>SNare it. </P><P>Dot the crap out of it .. watch it die. </P><P>Go loot tasty lewts frrom mob's warmn corpse .. OW SOMETHING HIT ME. </P><P>Invis up.. </P><P>RUn... </P><P>Feign off mob... mob goes to spawn point. </P><P>Invis up..</P><P>Kill some other named. </P><P>OR - *OPTION*</P><P>Aggro 18 mobs , invis up and train the *BEJESUS* out of the people who are in your spot... Listen to them holler about Where THE HELL did those come from..... </P><P>Most people don't keep see invis up.... </P><P>Watch 'em panic / watch 'em flee. It's good for a laugh. </P><P>I mean, If I'd ever done that... which of course would be wrong /and/or evil. <img src=icon_smile_wink.gif border=0 align=middle> </P><P></P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
